::Information::


Call of Atlantis: Treasures of Poseidon Collector's Edition


Genre: Adventure | Hidden Object | Match 3 | Puzzle


The legendary adventure is back! The power of Poseidon's treasures calls out to you, urging you to return to Atlantis once again. It now falls to you to find and collect all the lost treasures! Set out on an exciting new quest in this spectacular mix of Match-3, Hidden Object and Adventure. Embark on a fascinating journey around 7 ancient lands and collect 80 powerful artifacts of Poseidon. Appease Poseidon, the patron god of the Atlanteans, and save the legendary continent.
